Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: functions

    2 functions: function
    3          | functions function

    4 function: IDENTIFIER '(' parameters ')' '=' expression

    5 parameters: parameter
    6           | parameters ',' parameter

    7 parameter: INTEGER IDENTIFIER
    8          | DOUBLE IDENTIFIER

    9 arguments: expression
   10          | arguments ',' expression

   11 expression: IDENTIFIER
   12           | NATURAL
   13           | DECIMAL
   14           | IDENTIFIER '(' arguments ')'
   15           | IF expression THEN expression ELSE expression
   16           | expression '+' expression
   17           | expression '-' expression
   18           | expression '*' expression
   19           | expression '/' expression
   20           | '(' expression ')'


